imdb.plot outline: Annoying Orange plays Grand Theft Auto V (GTA V) as the infamous super hero, Buttman. He has unbelievable powers, weapons, and minions but still manages to create more crime than actually fighting it. Filled with crazy mods and hilarious let's play commentary.
